       <td>
	   <div align="left" class="storytitle">Review: Rome Total War</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storyauth">By Freonsmurf</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storydetail">Sep 28, 2004, 09:19</div>
    
       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=Review%3A%20Rome%20Total%20War&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Farticles%2Freviews%2Farticle_30.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="http://www.thesafehouse.org/articles/reviews/printer_30.php">Printer&nbsp;friendly&nbsp;page</a></div>
